overview: Delilah not only brings chaos and mayhem with her to this college, she also brings superstar Gina Lynn along for the ride. In the first contest, three lucky college guys compete in the Dirty Sanchez game (don't ask). Afterwards, Carly Parker, Kylee King and Anthony give a wild live sex show for the crowd. After students compete in "Brian Freeze". Carly is caught fucking a lucky college stud in his room and Gina Lynn and Anthony find a warm spot to bang the night away. With the beer bong still flowing, Delilah and Travis get going in the kitchen and it is then that a huge star is born! Carly is caught off guard by the one and only Shrimp Diesel. This college invasion is one that you won't ever forget!
title: College Invasion 13
